T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"20bc3e8ee123f2e0e8391d84e494d1fbed8389b1","tid":1727802,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:57:08.000Z","msg":"Pp"},{"pid":"bc6c59ad290360669421a64efe8a916f268803c8","tid":1727802,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58961d7822f3ac84c9511cb94aa4d244346bd1f5","tid":1727802,"uid":24306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd8a10c635f35abee90672ca69473d52d74a425","tid":1727802,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395b6f902b4366727c05b2a6ea70680fd850906e","tid":1727802,"uid":114080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"個重點係做主動 做主動人地先捉唔到你套路 每次都玩新野"},{"pid":"037cf6316e469ec76dafe5d43175317edbe5e110","tid":1727802,"uid":185057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2a82a81f817df52540704e6cc96bc1af06ef83e","tid":1727802,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcHhqFL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcHhqFL.png&h=86528844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n少少背景先<br />\n佢而家係一個Backpacker 四圍旅行<br />\n我同佢都係旅行坐火車識嘅。<br />\n佢由7.1我地爆入立會開始就一直關注。<br />\n佢地當年物資極難運入示威中心<br />\n所以佢地冇得用gas mark 所以佢地好擅長0gear抗爭<br />\n我地都落過場教過手足點用膠樽滅tg<br />\n<br />\n廢話唔多講 入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢前日打電話過黎屌柒我 有少少嘢想同香港人講<br />\n希望我冇記漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，你地嘅抗爭，全世界都見到，特別係我到處遊歷，你地令我感動嘅係，你地會救手足，而呢個情況係法國係好少見的。<br />\n<br />\n由11/11大學開花我就不停睇直播，即使我唔識中文，但我強烈感覺到你地為自由嘅掙扎。中大二橋一戰已經贏了，防止是需要嘅，但唔會令你地勝利。一隊足球隊有擋到99%射球嘅龍門，但冇人進攻第100球就會輸。希望你地明白，大學係自由嘅象徵，popo攻打，輸嘅係佢地。<br />\n<br />\n由幾個月前，你地成功進化挽遊擊，但而家popo都識打遊擊。敵進我退，敵退我進，呢句係香港人教我嘅。敵人都明白呢一點，保護大學，香港人入中大幫手，敵人明白到敵進我退，所以沒有再攻打。其次，呢個唔係打仗，唔係popo入黎插旗就贏，所以冇必要守。(我打篇文時，埋土冇人，班狗就開打，係敵退我進)<br />\n<br />\n你地而家要做嘅係，狗屋，狗宿，到新地方快閃，做主動，不是被動，只要成為主導就贏了。<br />\n<br />\nFlight for freedom<br />\nStand with Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"789月果時圍狗屋都係叫下囂<br />\n快閃狗屋又極難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af09f332a50aaf92d1b9a792e50bc5d8d2e94eb","tid":1727802,"uid":315864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"78a00cfd6219d1a3e4da8f046180420bbc08c656","tid":1727802,"uid":76514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"Highlight:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">銅鑼灣 Mr.eggcellent 係藍店</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUHYxsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUHYxsM.png&h=801fb44c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d73efe4db6deb4658e3b0e514a3cb11654121c8","tid":1727802,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00f80cbf5c9b34e22de940967e90a49aca24e57","tid":1727802,"uid":260598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"班狗郁啲就開實彈，點打？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"雖然呢個係事實 但咁講場運動都收皮啦"},{"pid":"1b8aed40bd35c09f928bf42a70dc92a198c5324d","tid":1727802,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6582d3540a0e931b4523ceaa59a30f839d073af","tid":1727802,"uid":37612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"推到前線手足睇到"